{"tw": {"3684690": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Bonjour, Cream Inside 💦", "steam_appid": 3684690, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "你只是個來自小鎮的男孩，懷抱著大大的甜點夢——這個夏天，巴黎就是你的遊樂場。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作為這座城市最具代表性的甜點店之一的烘焙學徒，你將製作令人垂涎的甜點，打動挑剔的顧客，並努力贏得法國頂級甜點師的稱號。但這不只是關於糖和麵粉……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/fb7dd586cab81dde9bcf140ffd9eba2a.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/fb7dd586cab81dde9bcf140ffd9eba2a.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/fb7dd586cab81dde9bcf140ffd9eba2a.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你住在一位富有（而且非常好奇）的遠房親戚所擁有的豪宅中，遇見迷人的咖啡館常客，並做出選擇，解鎖浪漫、火辣、有時甚至搞笑的故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/d7bc094b16b982daa0bbd7b74301197f.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/d7bc094b16b982daa0bbd7b74301197f.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/d7bc094b16b982daa0bbd7b74301197f.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>這是一款帶有點擊式玩法的視覺小說，充滿調情幽默、夏日氛圍和甜美成人內容。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍓 主要特色</h2><strong>純正巴黎夏日氛圍</strong><br>探索陽光明媚的街道、溫馨的咖啡館，以及浪漫現代巴黎的秘密角落。<br>🍰 <strong>甜點製作迷你遊戲</strong><br>混合、烘焙、裝飾——並給人留下深刻印象！你的廚藝不僅會贏得讚賞……還能解鎖更深入（也更火熱）的劇情。<br>💋 <strong>分支浪漫路線</strong><br>遇見各具特色、背景不同的女孩。選擇與誰建立羈絆——或是追求她們所有人。<br>🏡 <strong>豪宅生活</strong><br>和富有的表親同住？準備好迎接驚喜。打掃房子、做家務，或在下班後搞點“小麻煩”。<br>📖 <strong>按照你的方式遊玩</strong><br>專注於愛情、甜點或兩者兼顧。你的選擇會解鎖不同場景、路線和結局。探索這個調皮巴黎故事的每一種滋味。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/4591e5d6f4c67d4f5e195dbad2160388.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/4591e5d6f4c67d4f5e195dbad2160388.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/4591e5d6f4c67d4f5e195dbad2160388.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>", "about_the_game": "你只是個來自小鎮的男孩，懷抱著大大的甜點夢——這個夏天，巴黎就是你的遊樂場。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作為這座城市最具代表性的甜點店之一