"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 8 月 30 日"}}}}, "us": {"3684690": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Bonjour, Cream Inside 💦", "steam_appid": 3684690, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/00d200cc7e950e0cbf9f1175e705883c.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=227 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re just a small-town guy with big pastry dreams — and this summer, Paris is your playground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a baking apprentice in one of the city’s most iconic patisseries, you’ll whip up mouth-watering desserts, impress picky customers, and try to win the title of France’s top pastry chef. But it's not just about sugar and flour...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/228161d135367612a448d53552831c75.avif?t=1764609966\" width=598 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/fb7dd586cab81dde9bcf140ffd9eba2a.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/fb7dd586cab81dde9bcf140ffd9eba2a.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/fb7dd586cab81dde9bcf140ffd9eba2a.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re living in a luxurious home owned by your wealthy (and very curious) distant relative, meeting gorgeous café regulars, and making choices that unlock romantic, steamy, and sometimes hilarious stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/d7bc094b16b982daa0bbd7b74301197f.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/d7bc094b16b982daa0bbd7b74301197f.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/d7bc094b16b982daa0bbd7b74301197f.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a visual novel with a point-and-click twist, packed with flirty humor, summer vibes, and sweet adult content. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/9c1d03bf27ee68ad979a709314ec9e0c.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=235 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pure Parisian Summer Vibes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the sunny streets, cozy cafés, and secret corners of a romanticized, modern-day Paris.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍰 <strong>Dessert-Making Mini-Games</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix, bake, decorate — and impress! Your skills in the kitchen lead to more than just praise… they unlock deeper (and hotter) storylines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💋 <strong>Branching Romance Paths</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet unique girls with distinct personalities and backgrounds. Choose who to bond with — or chase them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡 <strong>Life at the Mansion</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Living with your wealthy cousin? Expect surprises. Clean the house, do chores, or get into a little “trouble” after hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 <strong>Play Your Way</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Focus on love, desserts, or both. Your choices unlock different scenes, routes, and endings. Discover every flavor of this naughty Parisian tale.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/4591e5d6f4c67d4f5e195dbad2160388.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/4591e5d6f4c67d4f5e195dbad2160388.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/4591e5d6f4c67d4f5e195dbad2160388.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/00d200cc7e950e0cbf9f1175e705883c.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=227 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re just a small-town guy with big pastry dreams — and this summer, Paris is your playground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/cff7c8e56d8e06f08a7418ceb2d1e542.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a baking apprentice in one of the city’s most iconic patisseries, you’ll whip up mouth-watering desserts, impress picky customers, and try to win the title of France’s top pastry chef. But it's not just about sugar and flour...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/228161d135367612a448d53552831c75.avif?t=1764609966\" width=598 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/fb7dd586cab81dde9bcf140ffd9eba2a.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/fb7dd586cab81dde9bcf140ffd9eba2a.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/fb7dd586cab81dde9bcf140ffd9eba2a.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re living in a luxurious home owned by your wealthy (and very curious) distant relative, meeting gorgeous café regulars, and making choices that unlock romantic, steamy, and sometimes hilarious stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/d7bc094b16b982daa0bbd7b74301197f.poster.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/d7bc094b16b982daa0bbd7b74301197f.webm?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/d7bc094b16b982daa0bbd7b74301197f.mp4?t=1764609966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a visual novel with a point-and-click twist, packed with flirty humor, summer vibes, and sweet adult content. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684690/extras/9c1d03bf27ee68ad979a709314ec9e0c.avif?t=1764609966\" width=600 height=235 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pure Parisian Summer Vibes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the sunny streets, cozy cafés, and secret corners of a romanticized, modern-day Paris.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍰 <strong>Dessert-Making Mini-Games</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix, bake, decorate — and impress! Your skills in the kitchen lead to more than just praise… they unlock deeper (and hotter) storylines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💋 <strong>Branching Romance Paths</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet unique girls with distinct personalities and backgrounds. Choose who to bond with — or chase them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡 <strong>Life at the Mansion</strong></p><p class=\